Name: Pattern Recognition - PE

Name: Inductive Reasoning - PE
Text: Synthesize the Process Flow: Global Sequence OR MS QS AS sub process TST loop skip PK choice LB DP D. Note LB skipped in some cases XOR after PK. RT TST loop structure. IQC AS interleaved loop before TST.

Name: Abductive Reasoning - PE
Text: Refining Model Structure Component B: Sub process before TST is loop AS then either TST or IQC AS again matching Case 4 direct AS TST and others AS IQC AS TST. POWL loop A AS B IQC: execute AS then exit TST or IQC then AS.

Name: Hypothesis Generation - PE
Text: Component C Post TST: TST then either PK or RT TST again. Loop A TST B RT then PK. Matches Case 2 TST PK direct exit. Case 1 TST RT TST PK one iteration.

Name: Validation - PE

Name: Hypothesis Generation - PE
Text: Component D Post PK: XOR LB DP then D. Case 2 PK DP D chooses DP. Others PK LB DP D chooses LB then DP but modeled as XOR to D.

Name: Deductive Reasoning - PE
Text: Constructing Code: Define transitions OR MS QS AS IQC TST RT PK LB DP D. as_loop LOOP AS IQC. tst_loop LOOP TST RT. lb_xor XOR LB DP. Root StrictPartialOrder nodes transitions. Add edges OR MS QS AS as_loop TST tst_loop PK lb_xor D.

Name: Validation - NE
